                        |  (apparently chipset is "TK102") is supported
                    li Why did I make this? Fun, plus I didn't want my GPS data going to some company in China
                    li This is a privately-run proof-of-concept done as a hobby. That's why it's so feature-poor =) You're welcome to use it, but don't expect much
